ew-calendar btn-hc\">View calendar</a></p>\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t<!-- Begin next collections -->\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"blocks block-your-next-scheduled-bin-collection-days\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"title\">Your next scheduled bin collection days</h3>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<ul>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li>Recycling collection (blue-lidded bin) <span class=\"pull-right\">1 January 2026</span></li>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li>Non-recyclable waste bin collection (black bin) <span class=\"pull-right\">8 January 2026</span></li>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li>Garden waste collection (green bin) <span class=\"p... [truncated]",
